  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ambassador of Japan discusses the current situation with the Mayor of Jaffna",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Japanese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Misukoshi Hidegi (29) called on Jaffna Chief Minister Vishwalingam Manivannan on Wednesday.",
        "Jaffna Municipal Commissioner ET Jayaseelan was also present at the meeting held at the Jaffna Municipal Council. The mayor also presented a memento to the Japanese ambassador.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Japanese Ambassador to Jaffna has been holding meetings with various parties regarding the current situation.",
        "Various issues were explored during this meeting. As the Mayor of Jaffna and on behalf of the people of Jaffna, I would like to thank Japan for the economic and development work that Japan has done in the past.",
        "Also during the period of peace in Sri Lanka, Japan made a significant contribution to the peace talks, especially with the Special Envoy to Sri Lanka Yasushi Akashi.",
        "Mayor Wiswalingam Manivannan also called on the Japanese Ambassador to the Government of Japan to present the Japanese Government's contribution to a permanent political settlement in Sri Lanka at present and to request the Government of Japan to use this opportunity to provide a comprehensive political settlement in Sri Lanka as a precondition for Japan's assistance to Sri Lanka in the current economic crisis."
      ],
